    <item>
      <title>二十国集团同意推动全球治理机构改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/g-20-agrees-to-push-for-reform-of-global-governance-institutions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过一个半月的谈判，二十国集团取得突破，同意推动联合国、世界贸易组织和多边贷款机构的改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/g-20-agrees-to-push-for-reform-of-global-governance-institutions</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 06:08:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丹麦首相称欧洲需要对移民采取强硬态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/europe-needs-to-be-tough-on-immigration-danish-prime-minister-frederiksen-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦首相梅特·弗雷德里克森表示，其他国家政府转变态度，要求采取更严格的移民管控，这是正确的。丹麦是欧洲移民法规最为严格的国家之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/europe-needs-to-be-tough-on-immigration-danish-prime-minister-frederiksen-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>小泉首相成为日本自民党议员选举的首选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/koizumi-ranks-as-top-choice-in-polls-among-lawmakers-in-japan-s-ldp-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民意调查显示，前环境大臣小泉进次郎在日本执政党总裁竞选中获得议员支持率领先，这增加了他成为日本最年轻首相的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/koizumi-ranks-as-top-choice-in-polls-among-lawmakers-in-japan-s-ldp-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 05:51:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>逃往朝鲜的美国士兵承认叛逃罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/us-soldier-who-bolted-to-north-korea-pleads-guilty-to-desertion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名从韩国越境进入朝鲜的美国陆军士兵承认了五项指控，包括逃兵和不服从长官，被判处一年监禁，他的律师在一份声明中说。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/us-soldier-who-bolted-to-north-korea-pleads-guilty-to-desertion</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 01:59:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡选举竞争激烈，IMF资金面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/sri-lankans-vote-in-tight-race-that-puts-imf-funding-at-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两年前，斯里兰卡的经济崩溃和历史性的债务违约引发了广泛的政治动荡，并导致前强人领导人下台，此次至关重要的总统选举最终结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/sri-lankans-vote-in-tight-race-that-puts-imf-funding-at-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚计划今年完成与美国的关键矿产协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/australia-eyes-completion-of-us-critical-minerals-pact-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯表示，澳大利亚有望在今年年底前与美国就关键矿产达成协议。]]></description>
